reliable full-duplex file transmission over half-duplex telephone lines.wa field-proven scheme for achieving reliableduplex transmission over a half-duplex communication line is presented, and to demonstrate the difficultyof the problem, another similar scheme, which is only slightly unreliable, is also presented.  a flowchartfor the reliable scheme and some interesting examples are given.cacm june, lynch, w. c..ktelephone communication, half duplex, transmission,error correction, full duplex, telephone errors.c. . .ca jb february ,   : pm